## Setup

To set up the project, run:

``` bash
git clone https://www.example.com/test/source
cd test
bin/setup

bin/hanami db create
bin/hanami db migrate
bin/hanami db seed

HANAMI_ENV=test bin/hanami db create
HANAMI_ENV=test bin/hanami db migrate
```
